<p>Here we go: It was a case of bottom's up for Bianca Gascoigne as she swigged from a champagne bottle while relaxing in a hot tub on Tuesday</p>

<p>With the picturesque venue's rural scenery serving as a backdrop, Bianca, 33, raised the large champagne magnum to her lips while dipping her legs into the warm water. </p>

