<p>She showed off her toned legs in a pair of knee-high white leather cowboy boots for the sizzling photographs taken on the porch of a white house.</p>

<p>Bianca wore her trademark blonde tresses in flirty curls round her shoulders and opted for a typically glamorous makeup look.</p>

